Everywhere Identity Matters





































								Identix							

 







Everywhere Identity Matters


							Contact Us						

							For Channel Partners						











Are they who they say they are?

When you need to ensure that people are who they claim to be—in person or online—we help you make sure. Using our solutions, we establish and/or verify individual identities through one or more characteristics. The more characteristics collected and verified, the greater the level of identity assurance. 








					Trusted Identity Platform
					


Trusted Identity Platform
The Identix Platform – a user-friendly identification and authentication SaaS that makes it easy for users to verify their identities in ways that feel natural, while offering the highest level of trust in online authentication.

Learn More

 



					Hosted Identity Solutions
					


Hosted Identity Solutions
Hosted Identity Solutions – Secure, online electronic identity credentials for high-trust transactions.

Learn More

 



					APIs and SDKs
					


APIs and SDKs
SDKs and APIs – Software Development Kits (SDKs) and Application Program Interfaces (APIs) verify and/or authenticate personal identities and identity documents.

Learn More

 



					Document Authentication
					


Document Authentication
Document Authentication – Document Authentication software and libraries for integration with third party platforms.

Learn More

 





















						Case Study
					
Mitek Systems
					Mobile Verify, Mitek's ID document verification solution, assures that the ID presented in a mobile transaction is a genuine, unaltered, and government-issued ID.  It provides consumers a fast and easy way to create a trusted identity with an organization anytime, anywhere.  Mobile Verify enables businesses to safely and securely acquire new customers and complete high-value transactions in the mobile channel.					
Read More 


 

Read More 




						Case Study
					
Confirm.io
					Confirm.io makes authenticating a government issued ID easy, fast, and secure. Integrate in minutes, and confirm a person’s identity for any transaction that requires or benefits from proof of identity.					
Read More 


 

Read More 








Why Identix

We are experts at relating real people to trusted identity records and in-person proofing events with our trusted and proven solutions.  Many multi-factor authentication solutions provide strong authentication but against a weak credential providing a false sense of assurance.  But not us.  We provide strong authentication against a strong credential.
Our Identification and Authentication Platform enables you to verify individual identities—everywhere identity matters.  With our solutions, people can easily prove to you that they are who they claim to be with a high degree of trust, wherever they are, and at any time.  The identification process can be adapted based on the level of assurance you require—allowing the right blend of technology and processes to manage identity risk while being cost-effective and providing the level of customer service experience people have come to expect in this digital age.
We leverage our experience as part of MorphoTrust USA which is built on decades of pioneering leadership in biometric identification, document authentication and data verification technologies, with deep expertise in all aspects of identity.











