TSA Chooses MorphoTrust Enrollment Solutions







Identity Services Brochure




 











Identity-Related Products and Services
Convenient, Professional Nationwide Locations
 
MorphoTrust has been providing fingerprinting services for well over a decade, building a nationwide network of enrollment centers in support of many state and federal agency contracts. Over the years, we have seen the need for a broader range of identity-related products and services to better serve the millions of customers that come to our centers. To meet this need, MorphoTrust launched the IdentoGO Centers to serve a growing number of consumers through professional, trained staff in comfortable, convenient environments. Gone are the days of  having to be fingerprinted in a police station to apply for a job or professional certification.
 
With our primary goal of excellent service, we have been adding new products and services to our Centers, helping customers cross more items off their lists in one trip. Offerings vary by location. Please visit www.identogo.com to find a location near you and check out the services provided.












Features & Benefits:


Convenient locations 


Fast and accurate fingerprinting results


Friendly and trained service agents


Online scheduling capabilities


 

 
 



















































































































































